<br>
So perhaps there should be some sort of time limit on the items so they will go Poof like a buff does after some period of time. That's probably some new bit of coding, but I'm sure there are other ways to insure the item is not used in an exploit of the game.  :)<br>
<br>
Though, it didn't seem to me that most of the people complaining about focus items were concerned about that. Common themes were that these 'items' somehow devalued current gear because people would (however temporarily) replace them with summoned ones.  Also, there was concern about the spell line concept itself pushing the abilities of casters to a level that would disrupt the game.<br>
